c: 13
v: 18
t: "KebonaabobalusabelayoubizolweNkosiyabo(ngokwamkela i-Islam) okwabo iya kuba kokulungileyo (iPaladesi) kodwa abo bangazanga balusabele ubizo lwaKhe (uAllâh), enokuba konke okusehlabathini ibingaba kokwabo, baze bafune ukunikela ngako konke befuna ukuzisindisa (esohlwayweni bekungayi kwamkelwa). Okwabo iza kuba sisiHogo; Hayi ukuba mbi kwaloo ndawo yokuphumla"